{"tid":1768089,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國勢力揭露支那間諜偷竊量子軍用技術","createTime":"2019-12-03T23:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T13:31:22.000Z","uid":47259,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1ded4891f35adea30535a6ff4e919f20678c5739","tid":1768089,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T23:32:19.000Z","msg":"盧比奧twitter見到<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gtlevesque/status/1201521097268551680?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgtlevesque%2Fstatus%2F1201521097268551680%3Fs%3D19&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDd9ps0HX4IqOCTpD1RfAd9E%3D&h=aceb4d20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgtlevesque%2Fstatus%2F1201521097268551680%3Fs%3D19&h=830ece1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/gtlevesque/status/1201521097268551680?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n要點<br />\nFor more than a decade, China has implemented an <br />\rintentional strategy to &ldquo;assign&rdquo; Chinese quantum <br />\rscientists to leading research institutes around the <br />\r\nworld, including in the United States, UK, Germany, <br />\rand Switzerland, to &ldquo;master cutting-edge research&rdquo; <br />\rwith the support of Western government funding <br />\rafter making &ldquo;unwritten agreements that they must <br />\rreturn to China after their studies are complete&rdquo; to <br />\rsupport PRC government dual-use quantum research <br />\r\nprograms. China&rsquo;s strategy has succeeded in <br />\rbuilding a competitive advantage over the U.S. and <br />\r\nother nations in certain quantum technologies with <br />\rmilitary applications.<br />\r\n<br />\nPan Jianwei [潘建伟] developed and leads this <br />\rstrategy. Pan, known as China&rsquo;s &ldquo;father of quantum,&rdquo; <br />\r\nis Head of the Division of Quantum Physics and <br />\rQuantum Information at the University of Science and <br />\rTechnology of China (USTC), which drives China&rsquo;s <br />\r\nquantum science collaboration with Western research <br />\rinstitutes alongside parallel collaboration with China&rsquo;s <br />\r\nmajor state-owned defense companies. Pan is <br />\ralso a concurrent part-time professor at Germany&rsquo;s <br />\rHeidelberg University.<br />\r\n<br />\nWestern Universities and research labs have been <br />\rcompromised at the highest levels. Pan and PRC <br />\rgovernment agencies have recruited a number of <br />\r\nWestern scientists with monetary incentives through <br />\rgovernment talent programs. Western quantum <br />\rscientists inducted into PRC talent programs include <br />\rMatthias Weidemuller, Dean of the Department of <br />\rPhysics and Astronomy at Heidelberg University, <br />\r\nand Barry Sanders, a theoretical physicist at the <br />\rUniversity of Calgary in Canada.<br />\r\n<br />\nHeidelberg University is arguably the most important foreign partner behind China&rsquo;s rapid progress in <br />\rdual-use quantum technologies. Over the past <br />\r\ndecade, Heidelberg University has provided physical equipment to USTC&rsquo;s quantum lab, trained, and continues to train, a generation of USTC quantum <br />\r\nscientists, and engages in cutting-edge joint research with USTC.<br />\r\n<br />\nPan and his team of quantum scientists at USTC directly collaborate with China&rsquo;s major state-owned defense companies and are behind numerous recent <br />\r\nbreakthroughs in quantum military applications. This includes quantum radar to detect stealth aircraft, <br />\r\nquantum magnetometers to detect submarines, and quantum key distribution (QKD) to enable encrypted <br />\r\ncommunications for the Chinese military, including on Chinese naval vessels in the &ldquo;far seas.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n支那不負男盜女娼之名, btw 又係德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cb84499c63241dba78fdf823ffb9a06ab29466","tid":1768089,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T23:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7f6f239b86f3fe83dc65806b6628458ef4e5a2","tid":1768089,"uid":186010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T23:39:07.000Z","msg":"量子軍用技術即係點"},{"pid":"b9bf53ca055a43dfa8b7026e56b060a62ef93df7","tid":1768089,"uid":232466,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"2d7f6f239b86f3fe83dc65806b6628458ef4e5a2","tid":1768089,"uid":186010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T23:39:07.000Z","msg":"量子軍用技術即係點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T23:46:38.000Z","msg":"詳情請參閱Antman電影"},{"pid":"06e7dd0c4a058c0d19778574754c13da44d93e2e","tid":1768089,"uid":153518,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T23:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2e449dcc5f8ce9620669f22b9c9cf420926e49","tid":1768089,"uid":72457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T23:58:44.000Z","msg":"量子通訊設備<br />\n殺拉登無延時直播個隻<br />\n秘密武器 一出可以將現代通訊更替<br />\n直接秒殺華為5g"},{"pid":"6f9be7d952c206dcb8412bbd8b90db3ae9a6554f","tid":1768089,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T00:39:16.000Z","msg":"支那本身有技術都要偷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0b6b79706aed2b63bb354ba7e122d9b24e0832","tid":1768089,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e2e449dcc5f8ce9620669f22b9c9cf420926e49","tid":1768089,"uid":72457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sc